  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function unichar_isspace(c: String): Boolean {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_unichar_isspace()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Determines whether a character is a space, tab, or line separator
(newline, carriage return, etc.).  Given some UTF-8 text, obtain a
character value with <link xref="GLib.utf8_get_char"/>.</p>  <p>(Note: don't use this to do word breaking; you have to use
Pango or equivalent to get word breaking right, the algorithm
is fairly complex.)</p>

